---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="border-t border-[#1e293b] bg-base">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-8">
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-slate-500">
        <span class="font-semibold text-slate-400">AI Hub</span>
        <span>·</span>
        <span>开源 AI 中转站信息聚合平台</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-slate-500">
        <a href="/about" class="hover:text-slate-300 transition-colors">关于</a>
        <a href="https://github.com/your-repo/ai-hub" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:text-slate-300 transition-colors">GitHub</a>
        <span>© {year}</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="mt-4 text-xs text-slate-600 text-center sm:text-left">
      本站信息由社区贡献维护，仅供参考。使用前请自行核实各中转站的实际服务和价格。
    </p>
  </div>
</footer>
